{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "14", "m": "06", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "22", "M": "57", "S": "29"}}, "news": [{"title": "Tight housing market boosts New York office conversions", "para": "New York real estate firms are increasingly converting office buildings into apartment complexes as an antidote to the city's housing crunch, tapping into tax incentives also designed to increase the supply of affordable homes. \"My belief is just about any building could be converted as residential,\"during a tour of an office highrise at 77 Water Street the firm is converting into a residential building. ", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/international/new-yorks-office-to-apartment-conversions-a-solution-to-housing-crisis/131715779?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-195782/131715779.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "international"}, {"title": "\u2018No power of review\u2019: Bombay HC nixes deemed conveyance to housing society", "para": "The Bombay High Court has quashed a deemed conveyance order, stating the competent authority lacked the power to entertain a second application on a finalized issue. Justice Farhan Dubash ruled the deputy registrar exercised an unrecognized review power, barring the second application by principles of finality and res judicata.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/bombay-hc-overturns-deemed-conveyance-for-andheri-housing-society-a-verdict-on-legal-finality/131716219?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-216822/131716219.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "Odisha government to introduce new act soon as it plans major shift in urban rental housing", "para": "Odisha is set to introduce the draft Odisha Urban Area Rent Control Act, 2026, replacing the 1967 act. The legislation mandates written agreements, caps security deposits, and establishes rent authorities and courts for speedy dispute resolution, aiming to balance tenant and landlord rights.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/odisha-to-revamp-urban-rental-housing-with-new-rent-control-act/131716191?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-154374/131716191.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}